{
  "stem": "268.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in this second camp already he was down to perhaps less than 100 pounds, maybe 90, 95 pounds.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was skin and bones.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When took showers-- when we were supposed to take showers in the evening.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And went to showers, I could see ribs, you know, count his ribs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And his legs were thin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And his cheeks falling in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then I found out they're liquidating the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I found out my father one evening told me-- we were working separate details.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He came into my barrack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He says, you know, I found my name on a list.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They're going to ship me to a different camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I said, oh, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he says well, you're in now so-and-so barrack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I was really scared then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew we were going to get separated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then the kapo told me, he says, you don't want to be barracked with your old man.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, he's going to pull you down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He says, he's about had it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're going-- didn't you see where they're going?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They're going out to meet their maker.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, to him it was like talking about making reservations to go to Vegas or something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He says, you know where they're going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said, my dad is among them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He says, kid, you try to survive yourself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He's going to pull you down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's all he talking to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I said to myself, how hateful.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "How hateful can you be?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I didn't listen to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I said, listen, maybe it's not true.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I wanted to go into that barrack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Then I heard rumors they're going to ship them out tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There must have like 50, 60 people there.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
